Menlyn Maine’s new R1.15 billion residential development, the Trilogy Collection, will soon launch its second phase which will add 157 luxury apartments to the market. The first phase of the development is nearing completion, with a total of 374 units expected to transfer to new owners in November and occupation expected on 1 December 2019. Phase 2 is scheduled for completion in early 2021 and will comprise 157 apartments. The full development will have a total of 531 apartments when completed. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-352905" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Collection-Front.png" alt="" width="930" height="550" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Collection-Front.png 1460w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Collection-Front-300x177.png 300w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Collection-Front-768x454.png 768w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Collection-Front-1024x605.png 1024w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Collection-Front-1200x709.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px" /> <img class="aligncenter wp-image-352903" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Collection-Back.png" alt="" width="931" height="550" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Collection-Back.png 1459w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Collection-Back-300x177.png 300w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Collection-Back-768x454.png 768w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Collection-Back-1024x605.png 1024w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Collection-Back-1200x709.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px