uite measuring 574 sqm. “This suite also offers a studio unit for staff accommodation, home cinema, climate controlled custom wine cellar, north facing terrace, private sun deck and swimming pool, two lounges and green spaces among other features. “This presidential suite, the only one-of-its-kind in the development was sold for R20.5 million,” the group said. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-352875" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Collection-Platinum-Lounge.png" alt="" width="930" height="550" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Collection-Platinum-Lounge.png 1462w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Collection-Platinum-Lounge-300x177.png 300w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Collection-Platinum-Lounge-768x454.png 768w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Collection-Platinum-Lounge-1024x606.png 1024w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Collection-Platinum-Lounge-1200x710.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px" /> <img class="aligncenter wp-image-352873" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Collection-Platinum-Kitchen.png" alt="" width="930" height="671" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Collection-Platinum-Kitchen.png 1198w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Collection-Platinum-Kitchen-300x216.png 300w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Collection-Platinum-Kitchen-768x554.png 768w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Collection-Platinum-Kitchen-1024x739.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px" /> <img class="aligncenter wp-image-352871" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Collection-Platinum.png" alt="" width="931" height="671" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Collection-Platinum.png 1197w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Collection-Platinum-300x216.png 300w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Collection-Platinum-768x554.png 768w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Collection-Platinum-1024x738.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px" /> <img class="aligncenter wp-image-352869" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Platinum-Bathroom.png" alt="" width="931" height="671" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Platinum-Bathroom.png 1198w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Platinum-Bathroom-300x216.png 300w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Platinum-Bathroom-768x553.png 768w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Trilogy-Platinum-Bathroom-1024x738.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px" />
